sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.END_TIME , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME , SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME < "12 : 00 : 00" AND COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME >= "08 : 00 : 00" AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 281 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
